WEBVTT

00:00.078 --> 00:01.475
<i>Previously on "Switched at Birth"... </i>

00:01.502 --> 00:03.840
<i>Bay: I found another job
working at that amusement park,</i>

00:03.856 --> 00:04.897
<i>Maui, Kansas.</i>

00:04.935 --> 00:05.949
I'm on games.

00:06.069 --> 00:07.125
Where's Lana?

00:07.148 --> 00:08.329
She took the baby and left.

00:08.368 --> 00:10.316
The nurse just told me
she had a plane to catch.

00:10.370 --> 00:12.779
We're engaged... to be married.

00:12.818 --> 00:14.640
<i>I wanted you to have this.</i>

00:14.961 --> 00:17.182
You can hang it up in Iraq,

00:17.175 --> 00:18.254
or Afghanistan,

00:18.309 --> 00:21.288
<i>or wherever "istan" you end up.</i>

00:21.717 --> 00:22.683
Hey.

00:22.718 --> 00:24.585
Oh my God, you're back.

00:25.888 --> 00:28.422
Don't ever disrespect
a girl like that again,

00:28.440 --> 00:29.473
do you hear me? Ever!

00:29.524 --> 00:30.725
- Ty, don't!
- I'm sorry.

00:30.759 --> 00:32.659
Where are you going?

00:32.694 --> 00:33.661
<i>I talked to Angelo... </i>

00:33.695 --> 00:35.429
he said I could stay over there.

00:35.464 --> 00:36.631
I don't understand.

00:36.665 --> 00:38.466
Why'd she go to Angelo's?

00:38.500 --> 00:41.369
I guess she needed some alone time.

00:41.403 --> 00:43.304
Can I stay the night?

00:43.338 --> 00:45.573
You can stay as long as you want.

00:47.000 --> 00:53.074
